    "lp_faq": {
      "type": "aliange-lp-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "q1": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What makes the Acne Protocol different from traditional acne treatments?",
            "answer": "<p>Most acne routines focus on <strong>aggressive oil stripping or antibacterial action alone</strong>.</p><p>This protocol is designed as a <strong>multi-pathway system</strong>, targeting:</p><ul><li><br/>Follicular congestion (comedogenesis)<br/></li><li><br/>Inflammation<br/></li><li><br/>Microbiome imbalance<br/></li><li><br/>Barrier dysfunction<br/></li></ul><p>By addressing all four simultaneously, the skin is treated as a <strong>biological system</strong>, not just a breakout.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q2": {
          "type": "question",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "question": "Will my skin purge when I start this routine?",
            "answer": "<p>Some people may experience a temporary 'purging' phase as the Transforming Exfoliator accelerates cell turnover and brings underlying congestion to the surface. This is normal and typically subsides within 2–4 weeks, revealing clearer skin.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q3": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What types of acne is this protocol suitable for?",
            "answer": "<p>Best suited for:</p><ul><li><br/>Mild to moderate acne (comedonal + inflammatory)<br/></li><li><br/>Hormonal breakouts with congestion<br/></li><li><br/>Post-inflammatory pigmentation (PIH)<br/></li><li><br/>Acne with dehydration or barrier impairment <br/></li></ul><p>Not designed for severe cystic acne requiring medical intervention.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q4": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How is this different from other acne products I've tried?",
            "answer": "<p>Our approach is unique because it's a comprehensive, multi-pathway system. Instead of relying on one ingredient, we use a combination of clinically proven actives that work together to address the various causes of acne, from excess oil to bacterial imbalance, for more reliable and lasting results.</p>"
